data.description: Welcome Home! This highly desired Condo in the Druid Woods community! 2 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms has all you need! This upper-level end unit, recently renovated kitchen with hand touch faucet, bathrooms to include replacing the main bedroom tub with a walk-in glass enclosed shower unit for easy access. Completely painted throughout, new luxury vinyl flooring throughout and new carpet in bedrooms, updated lighting, ceiling fans, including recessed lighting, brand new appliances, gas stove, dishwasher, to include full size washer/dryer and refrigerator! The split floorplan with spacious bedrooms offers privacy to roommates or perfect for an office or exercise area. The main living area has built in bookcases, great for pictures or favorite book collection, closely situated to a sunroom retreat with amazing natural sunlight and French doors opening up to a cozy patio/balcony located at the backside of the building facing a wooded area with no rear neighbors and privacy, perfect for morning coffee and reading. The community also has pool access, tennis courts, picnic/grill area and walking trails. Truly a must see to be appreciated! Conveniently located nearby major highways, shopping, entertainment, close to MARTA, Emory and VA hospitals, CDC, Fernbank, Whole Foods, and DeKalb Farmers Market! Please give me a call with any questions. Hurry, this one won't last long!
